              ><div data-instant-type="text" class="instant-rich-text itZpEhO2hvYPvXYOp"><h3>Can i answer and make calls with the Carbinox Blaze?</h3></div
              ><div data-instant-type="icon" class="iKOwnR9L3qyGprap3">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="instant-icon">
                  <title>plus</title><path d="M228,128a12,12,0,0,1-12,12H140v76a12,12,0,0,1-24,0V140H40a12,12,0,0,1,0-24h76V40a12,12,0,0,1,24,0v76h76A12,12,0,0,1,228,128Z"></path>
                </svg>
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="instant-icon" data-trigger="active">
                  <title>minus</title><path d="M228,128a12,12,0,0,1-12,12H40a12,12,0,0,1,0-24H216A12,12,0,0,1,228,128Z"></path>
                </svg></div></button
            ><div class="imNNKjIMi0Rv8dkA7" data-instant-type="accordion-content" style="--instant-accordion-content-height:auto;--instant-accordion-content-width:auto"
              ><div data-instant-type="text" class="instant-rich-text iMMrGpubbRe0Tnpsw"><p>Yes, you can answer and dial calls with your Carbinox Blaze. Just pair it with your phone and make sure Bluetooth is on.</p></div></div
            ></div
          ><div data-state="closed" class="id0PagqVNjLWT3QER" data-instant-type="accordion-item"
            ><button class="iN9qkuN29LFToU5Za" data-instant-type="accordion-header" type="button"
              ><div data-instant-type="text" class="instant-rich-text iLc5ncYQ2P2ZmUqDY"><h3>How does the gps work?</h3></div
              ><div data-instant-type="icon" class="ieMn6pFheFdzf8lPv">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="instant-icon">
                  <title>plus</title><path d="M228,128a12,12,0,0,1-12,12H140v76a12,12,0,0,1-24,0V140H40a12,12,0,0,1,0-24h76V40a12,12,0,0,1,24,0v76h76A12,12,0,0,1,228,128Z"></path>
                </svg>
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="instant-icon" data-trigger="active">
                  <title>minus</title><path d="M228,128a12,12,0,0,1-12,12H40a12,12,0,0,1,0-24H216A12,12,0,0,1,228,128Z"></path>
                </svg></div></button
            ><div class="i9Yt9kusrJHkMzc6c" data-instant-type="accordion-content" style="--instant-accordion-content-height:auto;--instant-accordion-content-width:auto"
              ><div data-instant-type="text" class="instant-rich-text ivrAxaDwchzGS1t2S"><p>To ensure accurate tracking of your activities, the GPS functionality on the Carbinox Blaze works in conjunction with the Carbinox Pro App. When you select any sport mode on your smartwatch, the device relies on your smartphone’s GPS for precise location data. This allows the smartwatch to accurately track your movements, speed, and distance during outdoor activities.</p></div></div
            ></div
          ><div data-state="closed" class="iPxt0r4TG0Iy2mXx9" data-instant-type="accordion-item"
            ><button class="iMCEJPXaD6UDTPnNa" data-instant-type="accordion-header" type="button"
              ><div data-instant-type="text" class="instant-rich-text iZrdvlPPvg36RsHKo"><h3>How does the ai assistant works to send text messages?</h3></div
              ><div data-instant-type="icon" class="ir4hrCfSrrtUwTRI3">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="instant-icon">
                  <title>plus</title><path d="M228,128a12,12,0,0,1-12,12H140v76a12,12,0,0,1-24,0V140H40a12,12,0,0,1,0-24h76V40a12,12,0,0,1,24,0v76h76A12,12,0,0,1,228,128Z"></path>
                </svg>
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="instant-icon" data-trigger="active">
                  <title>minus</title><path d="M228,128a12,12,0,0,1-12,12H40a12,12,0,0,1,0-24H216A12,12,0,0,1,228,128Z"></path>
                </svg></div></button
            ><div class="ieDtVGrPANBZ8Icps" data-instant-type="accordion-content" style="--instant-accordion-content-height:auto;--instant-accordion-content-width:auto"
              ><div data-instant-type="text" class="instant-rich-text iabUthW5EaVE1FD4K"
                ><p><strong>Access the Voice Assistant:</strong </p><p>Simply navigate to the voice assistant feature on your Carbinox Blaze smartwatch by selecting it from the main menu.</p><p></p><p><strong>Activate Voice Commands:</strong </p><p>Once in the voice assistant menu, tap the screen to speak.</p><p></p><p><strong>Send a Text Message:</strong </p><p>After activating the assistant, you can send a text message by saying the command, for example, &#8220;<strong>Send a text message to [name] saying [message].</strong>&#8221;</p><p></p><p><strong>Message Sent:</strong </p><p>The AI assistant will instantly pair with your smartphone and send the message as instructed.</p><p></p><p><strong>You can also make calls with the AI voice assistant. Just follow the same steps as the ones to send a message but instead, say "Call [name]".</strong></p
                ><p></p><p><strong>Important Disclaimer: </strong></p><p>While the AI voice assistant is highly responsive, it is also very sensitive. This means that in some cases, the message <strong>may not be delivered exactly as you intended.</strong> Always double-check your command to ensure it’s understood correctly. We recommend speaking clearly and confirming any important messages.</p></div
              ></div
            ></div
          ><div data-state="closed" class="iyrT8gLk6g3ednw7r" data-instant-type="accordion-item"
            ><button class="iflmcqp30d2yi1Bnb" data-instant-type="accordion-header" type="button"
              ><div data-instant-type="text" class="instant-rich-text i1gFU3FH6VB5bf3x0"><h3>Are the Carbinox Blaze watches waterproof?</h3></div
              ><div data-instant-type="icon" class="iw9AJ4DpEr2IAb9JJ">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="instant-icon">
